Nampak Wiegand Glass to Spend $75 Million Rebuilding Glass Bottle Furnace

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-07T07:27:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/nampak-wiegand-glass-to-spend-75-million-rebuilding-glass-bottle-furnace.html
Nampak Ltd. (NPK)  said Nampak Wiegand
Glass will invest 500 million rand in rebuilding and expanding
one of its furnaces at its glass bottle manufacturing plant at
Roodekop in  South Africa .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
